 />\n人地都係提出一樣嘢比大家討論,又唔係指手畫腳"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8fcb0835aac44f15cf1196d870b784f16dad2a68","tid":2488070,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"其實點解要去投白票啫？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2488295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2488295</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}